resources.description: Digital simulation and hardware driving used in analog simulator's design and manufacture can make the pilots a better visual experience of the flight instruments. High-performance dsPIC digital signal processor used for signal acquisition, control and computing. The implementing agency used one 4096 step/360 degree micro-stepping motor. The simulation test results show that, this method can vividly simulate the function of EGT instruments.
resources.name: EGT Analog Flight Simulator Instrument Method Research
